{"tid":749813,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"感冒有咩食療好？","createTime":"2018-07-20T10:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T03:55:47.000Z","uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3a265963926d93b468ff6a1a8f55b2c01417c6","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"早排睇到第二個post，啲連登仔話傷風感冒唔會睇醫生，會等免疫系統自己醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日男朋友返返下工面青口唇白咁返嚟，又頭痛喉嚨痛，仲湯左五次，佢話可能冷親，我話不如帶你睇醫生，落去買啲成藥俾你，佢話唔使，之後閂左冷氣大教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下全能嘅連登仔，呢個階段食咩可以幫下佢快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66869ce430523d1de6d56aeeb8132fe2dee609c0","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8ad16cd24e52470ca7ab6d966a93d57fc91ed98b","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"男友仲訓緊，落去買野整黑糖薑茶有無用？<br />\n上網睇食梨西瓜都有用<br />\n有無連登仔試過食生果有用？"},{"pid":"1457215592c9b06dea3daf45eb4ec2bcda90d01a","tid":749813,"uid":4293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"湯咗5次你肯定係普通感冒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d362d83b13800934e92fb65f11ff24d190825cd","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1457215592c9b06dea3daf45eb4ec2bcda90d01a","tid":749813,"uid":4293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"湯咗5次你肯定係普通感冒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"我唔肯定架，我都唔係醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢唔肯去睇，唯有諗下做乜令佢舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a55e371f26bff19c40265de2367e3c40527f8ba","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"佢琴晚同我食左2包營多同埋3隻煎蛋，我有啲懷疑係營多太熱氣出事，因為我一起身都有痰同埋喉嚨痛，宜家無乜野 無佢咁嚴重"},{"pid":"ee00fe13167ed13e4baddbfcdd12398d70e5cf08","tid":749813,"uid":142128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:43:26.000Z","msg":"飲酒"},{"pid":"2bdf08baea380c92ab53afca2885791252405b43","tid":749813,"uid":4293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d362d83b13800934e92fb65f11ff24d190825cd","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1457215592c9b06dea3daf45eb4ec2bcda90d01a","tid":749813,"uid":4293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"湯咗5次你肯定係普通感冒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"我唔肯定架，我都唔係醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但佢唔肯去睇，唯有諗下做乜令佢舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"湯咁多次 身體好易少咗水份而發燒<br />\n但如果佢其實係腸胃問題 飲水反而有機會會再湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉佢去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d309f3abc9853d95cbe266b8eaccc3607037a7e","tid":749813,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"湯左五次似食錯野<br />\n可能今朝食左啲污染食物"},{"pid":"eb5cc5444c7f46921d05b0219ba4527dbe8222a8","tid":749813,"uid":140870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdf08baea380c92ab53afca2885791252405b43","tid":749813,"uid":4293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":